{"id":171,"date":"2021-04-30T13:47:57","date_gmt":"2021-04-30T13:47:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aero.engindepts.wpengine.com\/?page_id=171"},"modified":"2022-09-01T10:25:32","modified_gmt":"2022-09-01T14:25:32","slug":"chairs-message","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/chairs-message\/","title":{"rendered":"Message from the Chair"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light is-style-diagonal-bottom\" style=\"min-height:300px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1144\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2149\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/aero.engindepts.wpengine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-scaled.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-scaled.jpg 2200w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-300x156.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-1024x532.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-768x399.jpg 768w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-1536x798.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-2048x1064.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-1193x620.jpg 1193w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-120x62.jpg 120w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/Texture-350x182.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2200px) 100vw, 2200px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\">\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center has-base-white-color has-base-blue-background-color has-text-color has-background\" id=\"message-from-the-chair\">Message from the Chair<\/h1>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"breadcrumbs \" typeof=\"BreadcrumbList\" vocab=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/\"><span property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"Go to Michigan Aerospace Engineering.\" href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\" class=\"home\" aria-current=\"page\"><span class=\"material-icons\">home_outline<\/span><\/a><meta property=\"position\" content=\"1\"><\/span><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-5\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\"><nav class=\" is-vertical wp-block-navigation is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-2\" aria-label=\"Navigation 164\"><ul class=\"wp-block-navigation__container\"><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item current-page wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/chairs-message\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Message from the Chair<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/mission\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Mission<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/history\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">History<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/facts-figures\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Facts &amp; Figures<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/fxb-building\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">FXB Building<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/seminar-series-ae-585\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Seminar Series (AE 585)<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/department-publications\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Department Publications<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/visit-us\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Visit Us<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/contact-us\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Contact Us<\/span><\/a><\/li><li class=\" wp-block-navigation-item wp-block-navigation-link\"><a class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__content\"  href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/faculty-search\/\"><span class=\"wp-block-navigation-item__label\">Faculty Search<\/span><\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:70%\"><div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default, ft-mt-two\">\n<figure class=\"alignright size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/04\/a-waas-portrait.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-250\" width=\"-398\" height=\"-398\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/04\/a-waas-portrait.jpg 600w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/04\/a-waas-portrait-350x350.jpg 350w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/04\/a-waas-portrait-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/04\/a-waas-portrait-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/04\/a-waas-portrait-120x120.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Anthony Waas, Richard A. Auhll Department Chair of Aerospace Engineering<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-base-blue-color has-text-color\" style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:1.4\">Greetings and Welcome to the University of Michigan Department of Aerospace Engineering. If you are looking for the leaders and best in the field of aeronautics and space, you have come to the right place. I have the great pleasure of chairing the very first aeronautical degree-granting program in the nation. Since 1914, more than 6,000 alumni have impacted the world for good and continue to do so today. You can learn more about the history of our Department on our <a href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/history\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/about\/history\/\">History<\/a> page.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our undergraduate and graduate aerospace engineering programs rank within the top five in the nation with US News &amp; World Report. With our award winning students, student teams, and faculty researchers, Michigan Aerospace will inevitably play a big role in autonomy, high-speed vehicles and commercial space, which will shape the future of aerospace. Our Department continues to learn and to grow a diverse community of faculty, students and staff. Many of our students serve on several Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI) student committees as well as our Department level DEI committee with faculty and staff members. We feel it is of utmost importance to hear the voices of our students and empower them to be advocates of change inside and outside of the classroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please continue to explore our website to learn more about our <a href=\"\/about\/mission\/\" data-type=\"URL\">Mission<\/a> and <a href=\"\/research\/\" data-type=\"URL\">Research<\/a>. In addition, do not be a stranger! You can always see what we are up to by visiting our <a href=\"\/news-events\/\" data-type=\"URL\">News Center<\/a>. If you do not have time to visit, consider subscribing to our newsletter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always stay safe and Go BLUE!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>\u2014Tony Waas<\/strong><br>Department Chair<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"past-statements-from-the-chair\">PAST STATEMENTS FROM THE CHAIR<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion has-icon-left\" data-active-element=\"none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Freedom of Speech Support<em> (June 19, 2020)<\/em><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>We value the rights of our incoming students to exercise their voices. We support our students who engage in lawful protests and use their voices to speak out against racism. Freedom of speech is a bedrock principle of our community and your admission to U-M is not jeopardized by your participation in lawful protests or exercising your constitutional rights.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please know that you are not alone \u2026 the Department of Aerospace Engineering at U-M is with you as we work together to eradicate systemic racism in our society. Below is a short list of resources and expressions from U-M faculty, staff, and students to help support our community through these unprecedented times.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/publicaffairs.vpcomm.umich.edu\/messages-of-outrage-and-hope\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">U-M messages of outrage and hope<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/publicaffairs.vpcomm.umich.edu\/undocumented-students-at-u-m\/#latest-statement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">International and undocumented students at U-M<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=G99u6z6CfM0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">U-M town hall: constructive conversations for societal change<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/enrollment.umich.edu\/supporting-students\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Supporting students<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/news.engin.umich.edu\/2020\/06\/perspective-now-is-the-moment-so-what-do-we-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Perspective: Now is the moment. So what do we do?<\/a>&nbsp;by Dean Gallimore<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/news.engin.umich.edu\/2020\/06\/black-computer-scientists-including-u-m-professors-call-to-dismantle-racism-in-the-field\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Black computer scientists, including U-M professors, call to dismantle racism in the field<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/news.engin.umich.edu\/2020\/06\/help-eradicate-the-virus-of-racism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Help eradicate the virus of racism <\/a>by Sara Pozzi<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/thegreenscholar.com\/2020\/06\/11\/a-call-for-authentic-black-engagement\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">A call for authentic black engagement<\/a>&nbsp;by Dr. Tony G. Reames<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The University of Michigan chapter of the National Society of Black Engineers has put together&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/document\/d\/1QNe6WGY-X431OD39GM7bCjxddd74e5rqAIDhFsYFsYE\/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">this list<\/a>&nbsp;of petitions to sign and organizations to support.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a concern about our campus culture, please report it to the&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/deanofstudents.umich.edu\/campus-climate-support\" target=\"_blank\">Campus Climate Support staff<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2014Tony Waas,&nbsp;<em>Department Chair<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Time for Change\u2014George Floyd <em>(June 2, 2020)<\/em><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Last week, I was deeply saddened to learn of the tragic death of Mr. George Floyd. My sincerest thoughts and prayers are with the Floyd, Arbery, and Taylor families during these most difficult times.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p>There are too many examples in our country\u2019s history of our police force treating people of color unequally. The pattern of racial discrimination, brutality, and fatal violence against black people must stop.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Our Chief Diversity Officer, Robert Sellers, has first-hand experience and openly shares his personal journey&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/odei.umich.edu\/2020\/05\/29\/i-am-so-tired\/\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a>. I firmly align myself with our university leaders who call&nbsp;on all of us to act on our scholarship and the education of our innovative faculty, students, and staff, to bring about change not just within the university, but in our broader society.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The only way to build a strong and inclusive aerospace community is to treat all people with dignity and respect, and listen to their unique, diverse perspectives. The department\u2019s DEI and Outreach committees are moving forward with unwavering resolve to ensure that our department is welcoming and inclusive.&nbsp;These beliefs are central to our&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/strategicvision.engin.umich.edu\/our-vision\/our-values\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">College values<\/a>&nbsp;as well.&nbsp;My colleagues Robert Scott, Project Manager for Special Diversity Initiatives, and Sara Pozzi, Director of Diversity, Equity and Inclusion, co-wrote an article that&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/news.engin.umich.edu\/2020\/06\/help-eradicate-the-virus-of-racism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">shows steps we can all take to the fight against racism<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please visit our&nbsp;<a href=\"\/culture\/diversity-equity-inclusion-resources\/\" data-type=\"URL\">Aerospace Engineering DEI Resources<\/a>&nbsp;for a list of student, faculty, and staff diversity, equity, and inclusion resources. Additionally, there are many University resources available to anyone in need of support at this time; I urge you to use them.&nbsp;Engineering students can receive support through the&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/care.engin.umich.edu\/\" target=\"_blank\">Michigan Engineering CARE Center<\/a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/caps.umich.edu\/\" target=\"_blank\">U-M Counseling and Psychological Services<\/a>. All faculty and staff can access services through the&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/hr.umich.edu\/benefits-wellness\/health-well-being\/mental-health-counseling-consultation-services\/faculty-staff-counseling-consultation-office-fascco\" target=\"_blank\">Faculty and Staff Counseling and Consultation Office<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Dear community, it is time for change. Please know that you are not alone \u2026 I am with you as we work together to eradicate racism in our society.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2014Tony Waas,&nbsp;<em>Department Chair<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:10px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull cta-pattern-3 has-expressive-purple-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-10\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group cta-pattern-3__headings is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-base-white-color has-text-color\"><strong>CULTURE<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-base-white-color has-text-color\">We are committed to a department culture that supports and celebrates each of our members in their studies and their work.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-outline-animated is-style-outline\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-base-white-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/culture\/\"><strong>Learn More<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column cta-pattern-3__image is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:60%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1095\" src=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header.jpg\" alt=\"diverse female aero students smiling\" class=\"wp-image-2034\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header.jpg 2200w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-300x149.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-1024x510.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-768x382.jpg 768w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-1536x765.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-2048x1019.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-1246x620.jpg 1246w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-120x60.jpg 120w, https:\/\/aero.engin.umich.edu\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/2\/2021\/05\/culture-header-350x174.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2200px) 100vw, 2200px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">David Hershey, Aerospace Engineering BSE Student, adjusts a plane that he is testing in the Aerospace Wind Tunnels in the Gorguze Family Laboratory on July 2, 2013. \n\nPhoto: Joseph Xu, Michigan Engineering Communications &amp; Marketing\n\nwww.engin.umich.edu<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Greetings and Welcome to the University of Michigan Department of Aerospace Engineering. If you are looking for the leaders and best in the field of aeronautics and space, you have come to the right place. I have the great pleasure of chairing the very first aeronautical degree-granting program in the nation. Since 1914, more than [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":11,"featured_media":0,"parent":17,"menu_order":1,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_genesis_hide_title":true,"_genesis_hide_breadcrumbs":false,"_genesis_hide_singular_image":false,"_genesis_hide_footer_